title: Hour 2 - Age Out or Fade Away?
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Age Out or Fade Away?
description:
Covino & Rich fill in for Dan Patrick and talk the return of Max Scherzer.. Mets wasted his outing. What are the worst wasted performances in sports? The fellas are intrigued by their producers dedication to the Lakers and they ask about personal performance in a game. Plus, would you rather be an athlete who ages out, or the musician where fans only want to hear old material? #FSRWeekends
